import React, { Component } from "react"; import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom"; import { toast } from "react-toastify"; import { logout } from "../services/userService"; class NavBar extends Component { onClickLogoutButton = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); console.log("logout clicked") logout() .then(this.onLogoutButtonSuccess) .catch(this.onLogoutButtonError) }; onLogoutButtonSuccess = (response) => { console.log({ logoutSuccess: response }) console.log("inside of success") this.props.history.push("/login") toast.success("Logout Successful") } onLogoutButtonError = (response) => { console.log({ logoutError: response }) console.log("inside of error") this.props.history.push("/login") toast.success("Your already logged out") } render() { return (
); } } export default NavBar;
